Module Descriptions:

1. Analytics Module
- Focused on data analytics and business intelligence
- Handles platform-wide metrics collection and analysis
- Provides user behavior analysis and ML-based forecasting
- Generates automated reporting

2. Research Module
- Houses technical and fundamental analysis tools
- Processes market sentiment analysis
- Generates comprehensive research reports

3. Social Module
- Manages activity and news feeds
- Handles community groups and messaging
- Implements trust and reputation systems

4. Financial Module
- Manages treasury operations
- Processes transactions
- Handles fee management and calculations

5. Market Module
- Tracks current and historical prices
- Provides market intelligence
- Monitors trading volumes

6. Trading Module
- Manages order processing
- Handles trade execution
- Tracks portfolio performance

7. Content Module
- Generates AI-driven content
- Creates and manages NFTs
- Provides interactive storytelling features

8. Games Module
- Manages contests and competitions
- Operates lottery systems
- Handles prediction markets and betting

9. User Module
- Manages user profiles
- Tracks user statistics
- Handles user preferences

10. Cache Module
- Maintains real-time leaderboards
- Tracks performance metrics

11. Marketing Module
- Affiliate Program Management
  - Tracks conversions
  - Handles revenue sharing
- Airdrop Campaign Management
  - Manages user targeting
  - Handles token distribution
- Marketplace Operations
  - Manages listings
  - Handles secure transactions

12. Models/Schemas
- Contains data models and schemas for all modules
- Ensures data consistency across the platform
